24 (10) "Eyelash artistry" means the process of attaching semipermanent lashes or eyelash
25 extensions to natural eyelashes;
26 (11) "Fixed salon" means a licensed, stationary, physical establishment where a
27 person licensed under this chapter practices cosmetology or any other service
