21 not apply to the instructional programs in cosmetology in the state area
22 vocational and technical schools;
23 (f) Set standards for the quantity and quality of equipment, supplies, materials,
24 records, and furnishings required in beauty salons, esthetic salons, nail salons,
25 and cosmetology, esthetic practices,[ and] nail technology schools, and
